[size=3][b]Alife Collection[/b][/size]
[list]
[*][url=https://www.moddb.com/mods/stalker-anomaly/addons/alifeplus-v1-0-01]AlifePlus[/url]
[*][url=https://www.moddb.com/mods/stalker-anomaly/addons/alifebalance]AlifeBalance[/url]
[*][url=https://www.moddb.com/mods/stalker-anomaly/addons/alifeguard-1001]AlifeGuard[/url]
